title: Humility

Have you ever considered that to lose weight you must humble yourself to your mistakes? Humility allows you to drop your perfectionism and in today's episode we learn that key lesson. By the way, the concept was given to me by a very special kid...my son. This episode is dedicated to Logan who has changed many women's lives in his unique way.
